            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿لَزُلْفَى﴾ لَقُرْبَى وَكَرَامَةً.</h2>\n<h2>﴿وَحُسْنَ مَآبٍ﴾ حُسْنَ مَرْجِعٍ فِي الآخِرَةِ.</h2>"
        },
        "41": {
            "verses": {
                "38:41": {
                    "id": 41
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿بِنُصْبٍ﴾ مَشَقَّةٍ، وَتَعَبٍ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿وَعَذَابٍ﴾ أَلَمٍ فِي جَسَدِي، وَمَالِي، وَأَهْلِي.</h2>"
        },
        "42": {
            "verses": {
                "38:42": {
                    "id": 42
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿ارْكُضْ بِرِجْلِكَ﴾ اضْرِبْ بِرِجْلِكَ الأَرْضَ لِيَنْبُعَ لَكَ المَاءُ.</p>\n<p>﴿مُغْتَسَلٌ بَارِدٌ﴾ مَاءٌ تَغْتَسِلُ بِهِ، فِيهِ شِفَاؤُكَ.</p>"
        },
        "43": {
            "verses": {
                "38:43": {
                    "id": 43
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿وَمِثْلَهُمْ مَعَهُمْ﴾ زِدْنَاهُ مِثْلَهُمْ مَعَهُمْ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿لأُِولِي الأَلْبَابِ﴾ لأَِصْحَابِ العُقُولِ السَّلِيمَةِ.</h2>"
        },
        "44": {
            "verses": {
                "38:44": {
                    "id": 44
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿ضِغْثًا﴾ حُزْمَةَ شَمَارِيخَ أَوْ قَبْضَةَ حَشِيشٍ.</h2>\n<p>﴿وَلاَ تَحْنَثْ﴾ لاَ تَنْقُضْ يَمِينَكَ الَّتِي حَلَفْتَهَا بِضَرْبِ زَوْجَتِكَ.</p>\n<h2>﴿أَوَّابٌ﴾ رَجَّاعٌ إِلَى طَاعَةِ اللهِ.</h2>"
        },
        "45": {
            "verses": {
                "38:45": {
                    "id": 45
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿أُولِي الأَيْدِي﴾ أَصْحَابَ القُوَّةِ فِي الطَّاعَةِ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿وَالأَبْصَارِ﴾ البَصِيرَةِ فِي الدِّينِ.</h2>"
        },
        "46": {
            "verses": {
                "38:46": {
                    "id": 46
                }
